incul (2.0.0)

  * New Features:
    - Replaced hardcoded password access with SSH key generation for
      container authentication.
    - Added backup functionality to export and restore container archives.
    - Migrated configuration files from .sh to YAML for improved 
      readability and parsing.
    - Updated list command to display source templates for each container.
    - Added per-container configuration to toggle visibility of menu entries.
    - Added XDG force-update to refresh panels without requiring a restart.
    - Expanded desktop entry discovery to include /usr and .local 
      directories.
    - Enabled icon pulling from containers via the sync script.
    - Implemented a more robust and user-friendly CLI.
    - Added support for inline Xpra arguments via configuration.

  * Refactors and Improvements:
    - Renamed primary binary from incul-manager to incul.
    - Restructured directory hierarchy and created a build script for 
      multi-OS support.
    - Refactored create-template, incul-init, and sync scripts.
    - Moved update sources and user creation logic to create-template script.

  * Dependency Changes:
    - Pinned xpra to version 6.3.6-r0-1.
    - Added support for Debian 13 (Trixie).

 -- Muna Bedan <munabedan@gmail.com>  Mon, 13 Apr 2026 11:30:12 +0000

incul (2.0.1)

  * Bug fix: 
    - updated sync to clean .desktop entries with sed to only keep required fields 
      to avoid cluttering the host Open With context menu.

